{"tid":2210290,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解「混吉」叫做「混吉」，出處喺邊？","createTime":"2020-09-20T09:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T10:17:11.000Z","uid":74094,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb147c9fa12caf3b2a75bc27127d74e3cbfc1277","tid":2210290,"uid":74094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"起源<br />\n<br />\n混吉一詞是出自老廣州的飯店、早期香港的茶餐廳或雲吞麵舖[1]，當時這些小型食館會用沸水做成清湯。而午餐肉、香腸這一類食物也會滾一滾給顧客進食，當年香港經濟差，物資缺乏，所以茶餐廳和粥麵舖就會用這些有肉味的水招呼客人，當顧客一坐下，茶餐廳侍應即免費奉上一碗這些湯水。<br />\n<br />\n由於當時有很多香港人三餐不繼，為求飽肚，這些人都會到這些茶餐廳佯裝光顧，當侍應奉上這些有味的水時，即一飲而盡，再趁待應不察時立即離開，以此得口有味的水飲。而由於部份中國人認為清湯一字意頭不好，「清」即「甚麼也沒有」，所以清湯又名吉水，取其意頭好，而這些茶餐廳有味的水也當作吉水招呼客人。當時侍應稱這些人：「混口吉水飲」，其後簡化為混吉[2]。近年「混吉」被香港人自創的另一句口頭語代替，名為「搞搞震，冇幫襯」，二者意義接近。<br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/混吉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%89&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omn4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=569fd090\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/混吉</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">唔知點解上面篇野有種似曾相識嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"aca15e6cd6d585edd445126b08513bd17cbfaafe","tid":2210290,"uid":9566,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"運吉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家啲人應該唔知啲鄉黑過年會運桔去人地鋪收錢"},{"pid":"a595ba1900b802272b2ed357ecef4f3c3d71ff40","tid":2210290,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"aca15e6cd6d585edd445126b08513bd17cbfaafe","tid":2210290,"uid":9566,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"運吉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家啲人應該唔知啲鄉黑過年會運桔去人地鋪收錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfda91f68895a9033e3722e9c858393ff60233b","tid":2210290,"uid":76854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aca15e6cd6d585edd445126b08513bd17cbfaafe","tid":2210290,"uid":9566,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"運吉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家啲人應該唔知啲鄉黑過年會運桔去人地鋪收錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"聽開呢個解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a93822d1d3eadad6860dd2f4799aacf0615c44a","tid":2210290,"uid":9566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a595ba1900b802272b2ed357ecef4f3c3d71ff40","tid":2210290,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"aca15e6cd6d585edd445126b08513bd17cbfaafe","tid":2210290,"uid":9566,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"運吉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家啲人應該唔知啲鄉黑過年會運桔去人地鋪收錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"擺低粒膠以為自己好威威?"},{"pid":"d762d7f0d7209484e83eb4ce33722e420ff1b4f8","tid":2210290,"uid":74094,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人一路睇上面篇野會諗起一乾三濕，硬係好似準備中伏咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b88d12cc714491a28e9052d28624d66c85b0db","tid":2210290,"uid":156913,"like":0,"disl